      "content": "hey im in dubai rn just got off a super long flight from nyc and i feel kinda weird. my chest has this sharp stabbing pain whenever i breathe in deep and i'm having a hard time catching my breath. i think all the travel stress is just giving me a massive panic attack... is that normal to feel like this after a long trip?",
